title: Alex Jones Show - 2011 Jan 23 SU [sebaygo1]
description:

The Alex Jones Show
Sunday, 23 January 2011


[sebaygo1]


The 2 hour Sunday show is typically a review of the past week's news and a look forward to the coming week's events.

The Infowars web site describes today's broadcast as follows.

On this Sunday Edition, Alex talks about Google's plan to change their algorithm to reduce alternative news sites' status to spammers in an attempt to control the flow of information on the internet. Alex also talks about the V for Victory campaign, the latest breaking news, and he takes calls.
